<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>handicraftsman • handy-man</xh5><p> <i>handicraftsman—</i>a man who earns his living by making decorative items completely by hand: His son inherited his own traits, and gave bright promise of excelling as a skilled <u>handicraftsman</u>.</p><p><i>handy-man—</i>a man skilled at doing small jobs such as household repairs: We had had this problem with our bath tub faucet for almost three months. First we asked a <u>handy man</u> to fix it.</p> </entry>
